# Shadcn UI

> Not a component library. A collection of beautifully designed, accessible components you copy into your project and own completely.

---

## Overview

Shadcn UI is a different approach to UI components:
- **Copy-paste, not install** — Components live in your codebase
- **Full ownership** — Customize everything, no library updates to break things
- **Radix primitives** — Accessible by default
- **Tailwind styling** — Consistent with your design system

### Why Shadcn?

| Traditional Libraries | Shadcn Approach |
|----------------------|-----------------|
| Install package, import | Copy code, own it |
| Override with CSS hacks | Edit source directly |
| Wait for library updates | Change immediately |
| Black box internals | Transparent code |

