## Key Patterns

### Adding Components

```bash
# Add a single component
npx shadcn@latest add button

# Add multiple
npx shadcn@latest add card dialog form

# Add all components
npx shadcn@latest add --all
```

### Component Structure

```
src/components/ui/
├── button.tsx       # Shadcn component
├── card.tsx
├── dialog.tsx
└── ...

src/components/      # Your custom components using shadcn
├── ScoreCard.tsx
├── CourseSelector.tsx
└── ...
```

### Customization

Since you own the code, customize directly:

```tsx
// components/ui/button.tsx
const buttonVariants = cva(
  "inline-flex items-center justify-center...",
  {
    variants: {
      variant: {
        default: "bg-primary text-primary-foreground",
        destructive: "bg-destructive text-destructive-foreground",
        // Add your own variant
        miami: "bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-500 to-cyan-500 text-white",
      },
    },
  }
)
```

